Description: Instant translation application
 LingoSnap is a desktop translation application that provides instant
 translation via global hotkeys, screen OCR, and terminal integration.
 .
 Features include:
  - Capture selected text with hotkeys for instant translation
  - Screenshot OCR for translating image text
  - Translation history
  - Multiple translation engines (Google Translate, Argos Translate)
  - Terminal integration for translating command output
